# ZirconOSFonts 字体来源清单
# 格式：字体名称  上游仓库/下载链接  版本  许可证

# === 西文字体（来自 kiwi0fruit/open-fonts）===
DejaVu              https://github.com/kiwi0fruit/open-fonts              master    Bitstream-Vera
EmbedSerif          https://github.com/kiwi0fruit/open-fonts              master    SIL-OFL-1.1
Inconsolata         https://github.com/kiwi0fruit/open-fonts              master    SIL-OFL-1.1
Lato                https://github.com/kiwi0fruit/open-fonts              master    SIL-OFL-1.1
LibertinusSerif     https://github.com/kiwi0fruit/open-fonts              master    SIL-OFL-1.1
NotoSans            https://github.com/kiwi0fruit/open-fonts              master    SIL-OFL-1.1
NotoSansMono        https://github.com/kiwi0fruit/open-fonts              master    SIL-OFL-1.1
NotoSerif           https://github.com/kiwi0fruit/open-fonts              master    SIL-OFL-1.1
RobotizationMono    https://github.com/kiwi0fruit/open-fonts              master    Apache-2.0
SourceCodePro       https://github.com/adobe-fonts/source-code-pro        master    SIL-OFL-1.1
SourceSansPro       https://github.com/adobe-fonts/source-sans            master    SIL-OFL-1.1
STIX/XITS           https://github.com/aliftype/xits                     master    SIL-OFL-1.1
Symbola             https://dn-works.com/ufas/                            latest    Public-Domain

